=Description=

Holger Eggerichs:

"INCUBATORS provide entrepreneurial teams with an environment to succeed. While traditional
problem solving and value creation often happens in enclosed hierarchical structures,
commons need an more open environment and provide a sense of belonging, through
communities, work ethics, and a wide array of services and resources."



